{"tid":1632252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好再爆舖住先啦，好嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:04.000Z","uid":182843,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0eaffccb42bfb4a079d3fa114cd6236dfb8e0ae4","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"利申不分化不割蓆不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">而家爆舖嘅程度已經足夠嚇怕晒所有藍店㗎啦，唔需要再繼續落去，再繼續只會係做多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔想再見到有啲仆街大媽/南亞賊趁火打劫，然後畀對家入晒我地數，我地自己人當然知道唔會係自己人做咁仆街，但出面嘅人唔係啊嘛，佢地一般唔會理前因後果，憑一張相就會有即時印象同評價。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外關於召喚神獸呢樣都搭單再提下，<span style=\"color: red;\">廢老廢中個頭入面裝嘅都係屎，頸位同頸以上嘅地方都好撚脆弱</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">要制裁佢地請瞄準菠蘿蓋同手㬹關節位</span>，只要廢咗手腳是但一樣，包保佢地收幾多錢都唔敢再出嚟作惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">我唔撚想大家再因為裝修呢樣明明只係支線嘅嘢嘈落去</span></span>，明明之前未開始裝修嗰陣仲好地地冇咁多分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家就因為呢件事不停有三毛出嚟話前線手足失控，又係咁想將裝修升級做主線之一。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一句講晒：<br />\n和理非：繼續集中返外國文宣，解釋返呢幾日嘅裝修同獅鳥嘅前因後果<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武嘅抖返抖，要快閃就快閃政府部門/狗屋狗車狗竇</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力！不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地已經睇穿晒林奠嘅手段㗎啦，唔好畀佢嘅分化陰謀得逞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同請推！"},{"pid":"a06f24f5c638102377e57def89b0ea4164ef9354","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"27e83d3dbf7d458844a4fd3a435049f843edff42","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"777681be618daefd9d95556ce165aa7dedeaa10d","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:05.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"e1748bd9086dc2d956d47a923413b04c88d02d44","tid":1632252,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"1dcadffe4e5fb185680fd629e5d78e3e1f25a897","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"563c98c509bafc9ab0e19306e0a01d001d81144f","tid":1632252,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"ＨＯＷ"},{"pid":"a632061aebf5423c73778b58c463689f66e8873e","tid":1632252,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"3966896d45bcb7382afbffabe9370333e314177c","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9db0007cdb4a7812650ba7b3b06205d841a370f7","tid":1632252,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d283b88ec79a0edcf6d94111b90da124e1ece80e","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c4aa955f7e5390d00de88cc7fdeaf8f0f373b0d0","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:07.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"880c2119934f80aee63d19c1630d3058322236cd","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:19.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"6dd997ea36bc7c898ff33e979772b49af55a1f9c","tid":1632252,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"好快會有風向撚話你係五毛分化狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeabbb1766c68312e60e179848fa489b7d1ceff4","tid":1632252,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0453848404d901556ac92e2d2afb18487fdf99","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"6a72905415d34523e7694f80d302e4978d001cbf","tid":1632252,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"又打狗？不了<br />\n根本冇人敢"},{"pid":"eb011939ed68a674c03148ee2a15e025a77e97c1","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f72dc3653d5700e7942904fac50d357bf18b05","tid":1632252,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋"},{"pid":"59c2861b3ab09560a197bad019a81085c6e01b1b","tid":1632252,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eb6af07bc3f952a19905a108aa71c13be566f3","tid":1632252,"uid":133235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"裝修警車風險大好多 尊重前線決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc812785e57896220826b4a35084c6f04160d2f","tid":1632252,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"[公投] 黎緊幾日勇武定和理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6be2b4ebbcc453358e39eb999c5afeb05dac9c9","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8f72dc3653d5700e7942904fac50d357bf18b05","tid":1632252,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"係，文宣一定要煲大緊急法嘅嚴重性<br />\n根本係林奠霸王硬上弓，緊急法本身推出嘅法律基礎同理據真係站得住腳咩？<br />\n淨係佢講嗰句乜鳩「引用緊急法唔代表香港進入緊急狀態」都夠寫啦"},{"pid":"7da1d3d8de6bb4eca8caa361f9f4958c8f468357","tid":1632252,"uid":149829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"紅色, 就係撐共撐警大集團。<br />\n美心, 吉野家呢啲其實唔可以話佢係黑, 最多係紅, 因為佢地係言論上攻擊抹黑示威者, 呢啲舖既裝修要停, 改為裝飾算, 另外starfuck裝黎意義不大, 因為平時都係比人hea多, 留番個地方俾手足入去涼冷氣, 俾同學仔齋溫書唔幫襯會唔會仲好?<br />\n<br />\n裝修黑色目標應該係黨鐵, 福建幫優品, 富臨系列, 建制派議員既地頭<br />\n黨鐵做殺人幫兇, 建制為多年禍害香港根源, 福建幫就真係出埋人去斬手足, 所以全部一定要裝修.<br />\n<br />\n至於藍色, 就係果啲冇乜影響力既撐共撐警小店"},{"pid":"cec9e648b8eedc9dd1118fb641ea2fb3db988ddb","tid":1632252,"uid":182843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"再推多十次"}]}